SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c02056045
Version: 1

HPSBST02536 SSRT100057 rev.1 - HP StorageWorks Storage Mirroring, Remote Unauthorized Access

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as soon as possible.

Release Date: 2010-06-02
Last Updated: 2010-06-02

Potential Security Impact: Remote unauthorized access

Source: Hewlett-Packard Company, HP Software Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
A potential security vulnerability has been identified with HP StorageWorks Storage Mirroring. This vulnerability could be exploited remotely to gain unauthorized access.

References: CVE-2010-1962

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.
HP StorageWorks Storage Mirroring v5 prior to v5.2.1.870.0

BACKGROUND

CVSS 2.0 Base Metrics
===========================================================
  Reference              Base Vector             Base Score
CVE-2010-1962    (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)       10.0
===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HP has provided HP StorageWorks Storage Mirroring v5.2.1.870.0 to resolve these vulnerabilities.

HP StorageWorks Storage Mirroring v5.2.1.870.0 is available using ftp:

